Here is how to keep only the first 5 characters of 'description' in the 'shortDesc' column:
```
// We start a SimpleDB instance
import { SimpleDB } from '@nshiab/simple-data-analysis';
const sdb = new SimpleDB();
// We create a new table
const table = sdb.newTable();
await table.loadData('./data.csv');
await table.updateColumn('shortDesc', 'LEFT(description, 5)');
await sdb.done();
```
